title: Friendly Ambitious Nerd with Visa
description:
I have been wanting to speak with Visa for a while now, and the time has now arrived! He has a book of his best twitter threads out at the moment titled Friendly Ambitious Nerd. We speak about this project and many wonderful tangents ensue 

Listen to Podcast version here: https://anchor.fm/podcast-9b57fe4/episodes/Friendly-Ambitious-Nerd-with-Visa-ef37s5

Visa's youtube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5S2d3Ue7wHn3PghiclcCqA

Visa's twitter: @visakanv

Follow me on twitter @AndreaLynnLewis
Email me here: andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
